	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.P.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum hic<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Unbekannt.</note>, qui has <persName ref="person74">Gastio</persName> nostro reddet isthuc<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">nach Zürich.</note> transmittendas, se recta <placeName ref="place97">Basileam</placeName> iturum significaret, meae erga te observantiae esse duxi, si te his longo post tempore salutarem, significaremque post meum a Gallica legatione reditum<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Vgl. <ref target="file12415">Nr. 2368</ref>,25-27.</note> hic me pristinae molae operam dare, ut scires, ubi gentium tuo prisco in me iure uti valeas.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam si unquam alias, nunc maxime meum illud erga te studium viget; quod re potius quam verbis testari recipio.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Certe, si cuiusquam, tui maxime, causa nihil non conabor, mi Bullingere, et, ut periculum facias, te etiam atque etiam rogo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div2" corresp="regest2">
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim serva te nobis incolumem, nam quamdiu vixeris, tandiu et literariae reipublicae et christiano nomini consultum iri arbitramur.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego (quod mihi tantum licet)<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">Klammern <hi>ergänzt.</hi></note> quotidie te in tuis scriptis disserentem audio et pene conspicor.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Inprimisque sum tuis defensionibus mirabiliter delectatus.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Summam enim illae doctrinam et illam, quam ego maxime probo, egregie redolent animi moderationem<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Zu diesen Büchern Bullingers siehe bereits <hi>HBBW</hi> XV 378 und Anm. 7.</note>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Annotationum tuarum<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Offensichtlich hatte Bullinger ihm auch noch seinen im August 1545 erschienenen Markuskommentar <hi>(VD16</hi> B4904; HBBibl I 170) zukommen lassen, zusammen mit einem nicht erhaltenen Brief, der auf <hi>HBBW</hi> XV, <ref target="file12234">Nr. 2187</ref>, vom 22. Juni 1545 antwortete.</note> iam bonam perlegi partem.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene atque optime vale, et me in tuo aere<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><hi><persName ref="person632">Cicero</persName>,</hi> Epistulae ad familiares, 15, 14, 1.</note> semper censeas et, ut vales et si quid novi excudis, significes quandoque, rogo atque obsecro.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iterum vale.<pb type="edition" next="263"/></s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div3" corresp="regest3">
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Datum Nozerethi, 8. calendas aprilis anno christiano 1546.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tui studiosissimus et observandissimus</s>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div xml:id="div4" corresp="regest4">
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person20061">Gilbertus</persName> Cognatus Nozerenus<ptr target="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"/>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person20120">Conradum Gesnerum</persName>, medicum excellentem, cuius opus Bibliotheces<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="person20120">Gessners</persName> Bibliotheca universalis sive catalogus omnium scriptorum locupletissimus, in tribus linguis, Latina, Graeca, et Hebraica Zürich, <persName ref="person891">Christoph Froschauer</persName>, 1545 <hi>(VD16</hi> G 1698; <hi>BZD</hi> C350).</note> nondum mihi contingere nec videre licuit, <persName ref="person14">Bibliandrum</persName>, <persName ref="person165">Pellicanum</persName> caeterosque ecclesiastes salvere iubeo<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>Links neben der Unterschrift nachgetragen.</hi></note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro domino Henrico Bullingero theologo, praeceptori suo suspiciendo.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
